para_trans: To bring to the notice of the circular of the Government of India
Government Circular No: Income Tax 2025 / Q. 09/25 Treasuries-5
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk
Reference: Circular No. 3/2025 F No. 275/107/2024 - IT (B), D. 20.02. 2025.

Detailed instructions on income tax deduction for the financial year 2024-2025 (Tax Assessment Year 2025 - 2026) have been issued by the circular under the reference of the Government of India. The circular is available on the Government of India's www.incometaxindia.gov.in website along with its accompanying supporting documents.
All the Ministries / Administrative Departments / Heads of Departments / Heads of Offices shall take necessary action as per the aforesaid circular of the Government of India.
This Government Circular is available on the website of the Government of Maharashtra www.maharashtra.gov.in.
